<item>
            <title>[SEC-286] log4j should have optional scope</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-286</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Maven2 POM lists log4j with default scope which has the affect of adding the log4j-1.2.9.jar to my webapp.  Unless log4j is explictly used by Acegi (which it shouldn&apos;t), please change the scope to optional.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
